  "body": "As an extension to https://github.com/ConsenSys/teku/pull/6167 and https://github.com/ConsenSys/teku/issues/6142 we can improve the `FailoverValidatorApiHandler` to not send requests to a BN if it is not synced. \r\n\r\nCurrent solution is still viable since the BN will return `503 Beacon node is currently syncing and not serving request on that endpoint` for most calls and will failover after the exception, but there will be loads of unnecessary calls, which will slow down the validator duties completion.",
